{"tid":2258112,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[Mildom] 日本妹大戰支那女人 (有圖)","createTime":"2020-10-25T18:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T18:35:49.000Z","uid":88300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c01957893295dd69b39bfcdd7d40a73c334e4e07","tid":2258112,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RHe93Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RHe93Z.jpg&h=434d5da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我都唔知佢地乜水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"x-large\">成日睇日本野嘅人要留意返啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係想提醒大家Mildom呢個直播平台係由<span class=\"red\">武漢闘魚網絡科技有限公司</span>同<span class=\"teal\">三井物産</span> (三井住友銀行果間公司) 一齊設立嘅株式会社<span class=\"red\">DouYu Japan</span>營運<br />\n<br />\n屌, 咁撚長<br />\n即係<span class=\"xx-large\">Mildom = 闘魚</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mildom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fja.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMildom&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=a91f9bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mildom</a><br />\n<br />\n闘魚係中國一個直播平台, 啲中國人好似會喺呢度背著祖國熱烈支持日本節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返Mildom <br />\n好多日本名人喺呢個平台直播打機果類<br />\n睇睇下Youtube突然叫人轉場去Mildom, 好撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家睇路<br />\n<br />\n抗日小粉紅們可以放心睇啦, 唔係小日本野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMildom = 闘魚 = 啲錢係比中國賺嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f3d6e7f571443e43b85487409c84eb9d44a1a3","tid":2258112,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed4339d3c282e7a4b9e4a694305f7b0d7fe1615","tid":2258112,"uid":15646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:29:42.000Z","msg":"豬西vs豬西+大陸網=不了"},{"pid":"95ef801f2bebb7e5a904eef1feff8d5a701cfe54","tid":2258112,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:35:49.000Z","msg":"日本好多野都被滲透得好勁"}]}